## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of sources and the scope of the search, which primarily focused on online resources. The dynamic and evolving nature of societies means that definitions and characteristics can vary across different cultural and academic contexts. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources may not capture the full complexity of sociological theories and perspectives. Further research, including primary data collection and analysis, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of what constitutes a society.